open-source development.

## Technical Highlights

- **Performance**: 3,720 req/s gateway, 100 concurrent connections @ 1.72ms p95 latency
- **Threading**: 8-thread HTTP server pool with validated load testing (k6)
- **Modern C++**: C++17/C++20, RAII, move semantics, smart pointers
- **DevOps**: Docker Compose, CI/CD (GitHub Actions), automated documentation (Doxygen)
- **Testing**: GoogleTest (unit), k6 (load), Visual Studio profiler (CPU analysis)
- **Documentation**: 8,000+ lines (architecture guides, profiling, interview prep)
